data.text:
Rachel Withers

Broker | REALTOR ®

Mobile

919-523-7049

Social

What Does Being a Part of The Jim Allen Group Mean to You?

Taking my business to the next level. The systems and structure at JAG allow me to give my clients a high level of service. A team atmosphere where we help each other.

How Long Have You Called North Carolina Home?

My family moved from Buffalo, NY to NC when I was in the 2nd grade.

If You Had Unlimited Time and Resources, How Would You Spend Your Days?

I would still be a Realtor and help people become homeowners. I would volunteer at my local charities. I would also serve in more demanding roles at my Realtor Association and train new agents.

What’s Your Favorite Local Restaurant?

Rudinos Rooftop. I love sitting on the rooftop on a warm day, enjoying good food and friends.

The Cesar salad and margarita flatbread pizza are my favorites. They have a good variety of local beers on tap, and everyone knows my name.

How Would You Describe Yourself in One Word, and Why?

Fun- I love having a good time with my friends and family.

Asheville or Wilmington?

Wilmington. Blue water, close to the Beach, and sunny days.

What Causes/Charities Do You Care About?

Dorcas Ministries – sponsor a shelf at their food pantry.

Designed for Joy – Corporate Sponsor and Shelf sponsor

Who are the People (and Pets) that Keep You Motivated?

My sons- Aiden and Liam.

Rachel was making my selling/buying homes easy and smooth transactions. Carolina T.

Rachel was great I have already referred her to others. With my crazy work hours she was always available to answer my many questions. I definitely recommend her. Veronica R.

Rachel was fantastic to work with. I've worked with her twice now, once as a first time home buyer then later as a seller to sell that house. Each time she was knowledgable, organized, thoughtful, professional and very patient with my many questions (Sorry Rachel!!!) She also has a fantastic list of contacts and resources I was able to tap into for pre/post sale needs like home inspections, repairs, painting etc. Rachel is an absolute asset. Jennifer V.
